overview: The 16th volume of this acclaimed series finds stunning black girls and gorgeous white girls in the throes of interracial passion. College student Karlie Montana gets seriously schooled by Ethnic Studies professor Anya Ivy, and the lesson is a hot one! Winsome blond Elsa Jean invites new student Adrian Maya over to study and discovers that she and Adrian have a lot in common. R&B diva Yasmine DeLeon is home sick after canceling some concerts, and puts her assistant Penny Pax through the ringer! Penny sticks up for herself, and the results are steamy. Finally, personal trainers and rivals Kira Noir and Kelsi Monroe go head to head in a turf war, and battle it out till the very end.
title: Lesbian Beauties 16: Interracial
